  "description": "<p>微软一直在对自家的云服务产品不停地进行各方面细致的修改。<strong>最近又有传言称微软预备为SkyDrive站点添设可让用户查看最近上传文件的功能。</strong>国外媒体引用未具名的消息来源称，这里所称的“近期活动”新特性不仅能够让用户在SkyDrive.com看到最新上传和建立的文件与文件夹，也能展示最近用户和 其他人分享的文件，而且也会指出哪些文件近期被修改，哪些文档被打开过。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e1a8c59/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243220.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A0SkyDrive.com%E5%B0%86%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E2%80%9C%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E2%80%9D%E6%96%B0%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7+%E5%8F%AF%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243220.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A0SkyDrive.com%E5%B0%86%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E2%80%9C%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E2%80%9D%E6%96%B0%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7+%E5%8F%AF%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243220.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A0SkyDrive.com%E5%B0%86%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E2%80%9C%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E2%80%9D%E6%96%B0%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7+%E5%8F%AF%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243220.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A0SkyDrive.com%E5%B0%86%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E2%80%9C%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E2%80%9D%E6%96%B0%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7+%E5%8F%AF%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%